other_info: 讨论的论文为'AICoderEval: Improving AI Domain Code Generation of Large Language Models'，用户对该论文表示认可；对论文 'mHumanEval -- A Multilingual Benchmark to Evaluate Large Language Models for Code Generation' 感到满意；对论文'CodeMixBench: Evaluating Large Language Models on Code Generation with Code-Mixed Prompts'感到满意，理由是聚焦通用代码生成的现实问题，关注代码混合提示在实际开发中的常见性；对论文 'Aligning Crowd-sourced Human Feedback for Reinforcement Learning on Code Generation by Large Language Models' 感到满意并认可；之前淘汰过Verilog相关的论文；认可的框架：Brainstorming框架（让LLM先生成多种思路再选择最优路径）；对论文'Large Language Model-Aware In-Context Learning for Code Generation'感到满意，认可其聚焦通用代码生成的核心优化路径（ICL示例选择）；对论文'What Makes Large Language Models Reason in (Multi-Turn) Code Generation?'感到满意，认可其系统性地研究提示策略在多轮代码生成中的作用机制。
